// DESIGN DECISION — no separate `Agency` table.
// LAUNCH_READINESS_ROADMAP §4 lists `agencies` as a table and §5 says external
// users are "scoped to one company or agency". The implemented design (see
// lib/mock-services/agencyService.ts: `type Agency = Company & { meta }`) models
// agencies as Company records of `type = agency`, joined with partner-network
// metadata — NOT as a distinct entity. External users therefore scope to a
// Company (which may be an agency) via User.companyId; no agencyId FK is needed.
// Roadmap §4's `agencies` line should be read as "agency-typed companies".
